What is Real Life Squid Game Albania?
Real Life Squid Game Albania  (SGA)– University Edition is a fun and competitive event where students take on a series of challenging games. It will be held at Epoka University Campus on April 30, 2025 and is open to Epoka students and high schoolers.

Is this a simulation, advertisement or it will be really organized?
Hundreds of players, 5000m2 field of 10 best Squid and Albanian Games, one big PRIZE to win :)

Are the applications open?
Yes the applications are still open and can be accessed through www.lojtarifundit.com/apply

Who can apply?
We aim to involve all students, but due to limited spots for 2025, applications are currently open to EPOKA and high school students. If we there will be more spots available in upcoming days, we will announce in our social medias!

►Date and time?
April 30, 2025 from 14.00 - Midnight

►Under 18 years old?
You must submit the:
The declaration form, signed by a parent or legal guardian (DOWNLOAD THE FORM HERE)
A copy of your ID card + parent/guardian’s ID card (printed both in one A4).

►Coming from other regions than Tirana?
Unfortunately you must ensure transportation from Tirana center to your hometown. Our team will be able to send you from Epoka Campus to Tirana center by the latest bus (midnight)
 
Is the REGISTRATION for FREE?
Unfortunately NOT! As a "from students to students activity" this event required registration ticket to be part of SGA - 2025 [check apply tab].

Is there any winning PRIZE?
Fortunately YES! We are pleased to share with you that there will be $1000 prize for one winner (The final player - Lojtari Fundit).

Will the games be same as Netflix Squid Games?
The SGA Team is looking to organize most of the games similar as Squid Game 1 and 2.
